---
import SectionLabel from "../../../elements/SectionLabel.astro";
import Heading from "../../../elements/Heading.astro";
---

<section class="py-32 md:py-48 px-6 bg-rh-warm-light dark:bg-rh-warm-dark">
  <!-- Terminal Header -->
  <SectionLabel text="> SYS.DEPLOYMENT // THE_PROTOCOL" centered class="mb-6" />

  <!-- Headline -->
  <Heading centered class="mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    How We Build<br />Your Moat.
  </Heading>

  <!-- 3-Step Grid -->
  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12"
  >
    <!-- Card 01: Infrastructure & AI -->
    <div
      class="p-8 lg:p-10 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-4xl bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 relative group hover:border-rh-ember/50 transition-colors duration-500"
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-rh-ink/20 dark:text-rh-chalk/20 mb-6 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-500"
      >
        01
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk mb-4"
      >
        Strategy & Architecture
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
        We audit your existing ecosystem and architect a custom blueprint
        matched to your actual operational capacity. This includes engineering
        new business models designed to <strong
          class="font-bold text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk"
          >turn raw attention into a self-sustaining asset.</strong
        >
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 02: Culture & Rituals -->
    <div
      class="p-8 lg:p-10 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-4xl bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 relative group hover:border-rh-ember/50 transition-colors duration-500"
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-rh-ink/20 dark:text-rh-chalk/20 mb-6 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-500"
      >
        02
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk mb-4"
      >
        Supporting Systems
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
        A blueprint is only as good as the machine running it. We deploy the
        technical platforms, AI automations, and operational workflows required
        to support the vision, and then <strong
          class="font-bold text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk"
          >train your team to operate the ecosystem flawlessly.</strong
        >
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 03: Monetization & Scale -->
    <div
      class="p-8 lg:p-10 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 rounded-4xl bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 relative group hover:border-rh-ember/50 transition-colors duration-500"
    >
      <div
        class="font-mono text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-rh-ink/20 dark:text-rh-chalk/20 mb-6 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-500"
      >
        03
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk mb-4"
      >
        Culture & Scale
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed">
        We launch the environment and relentlessly measure the data. We validate
        the rituals directly with your community, refactoring the human feedback
        loops <strong class="font-bold text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk"
          >so the culture scales predictably, with or without you.</strong
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Output Readout Block: Data Matrix -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-24 lg:mt-32">
    <SectionLabel text="> SYSTEM_OUTPUT // EXPECTED_ROI" class="mb-6 px-6" />

    <div
      class="border-y border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 bg-black/2 dark:bg-white/2"
    >
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x divide-black/10 dark:divide-white/10"
      >
        <div
          class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-rh-chalk/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
            >&gt; METRIC_01</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-300"
            >Defensible Culture</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed"
            >Zero reliance on algorithm churn. Your people stay for each other.</span
          >
        </div>

        <div
          class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-rh-chalk/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
            >&gt; METRIC_02</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-300"
            >Maximized LTV</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed"
            >Members who stick around compound your retention and easily
            upgrade.</span
          >
        </div>

        <div
          class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-rh-chalk/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
            >&gt; METRIC_03</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-300"
            >Network Effects</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed"
            >Organic, high-ticket referrals driven entirely by peer-to-peer
            advocacy.</span
          >
        </div>

        <div
          class="p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col group hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors duration-300"
        >
          <span
            class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-rh-chalk/40 mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase"
            >&gt; METRIC_04</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk uppercase tracking-tighter mb-3 group-hover:text-rh-ember transition-colors duration-300"
            >Predictable ARR</span
          >
          <span
            class="text-sm md:text-base text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-rh-chalk/70 leading-relaxed"
            >A self-sustaining engine that compounds revenue without burning out
            the founder.</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
